snippet: Ali Charaf Damache, a dual Algerian and Irish citizen, was arrested in Barcelona and is accused of planning to set up terrorist training camps and kill several Westerners.
abstract: Spanish officials arrest Ali Charaf Damache, who United States suspects of terrorist activity.
lead_paragraph: Ali Charaf Damache, a dual Algerian and Irish citizen, was arrested in Barcelona and is accused of planning to set up terrorist training camps and kill several Westerners.

headline.main: Spain Arrests Terrorism Suspect in Plot Against Swedish Artist
